    "persona intent is a new component. It is the interface between the persona mind and the psyche. … it is the apex, the most powerful part, notwithstanding the supervisor, which only has higher permission because it's an infrastructure component that's there to make sure the engine is running. … it would be the last one to start. It's a sort of persona mind of its own, but it's specialized on the psyche, on keeping track of the psyche."
