(Decision
    "An intent entry can be restated and therefore owns multiple verbatim references. The verbatim field is a vector of timestamped structs rather than one flat quote string."
    "every intent, because it can be restated, can have multiple verbatim references. So that the verbatim object is going to be a vector, and that because every verbatim entry is going to have a timestamp, it's going to be a struct."
    "Defining the first typed persona-spirit intent-entry record shape, replacing the crude manual file schema."
    Maximum
    2026-05-19T13:08:11Z)

